This list chronicles the properties and districts within [Scotland County, North Carolina](/Scotland_County,_North_Carolina) that have been officially recognized and inscribed on the [National Register of Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places). The coordinates for these significant locations have been meticulously mapped and are available for viewing via an interactive online map, accessible through the provided link.&#91;1&#93;

The compilation of this register is an ongoing endeavor, managed by the [National Park Service](/National_Park_Service). The data presented here reflects the most recent updates to the list, as of December 12, 2025.&#91;2&#93; It’s a testament to the enduring legacy of history preserved in brick, mortar, and the very landscape of the county.

